{
  "texts": [
    "Surprisingly, the spike-in control strains I. halotolerans and A. halotolerans were also linked to an ARG, while the reference genomes do not contain any.",
    "In sample B, the oqxAB operon was linked to K. pneumoniae, while qnrS1 was associated to plasmids (Figure 2D).",
    "Similar to sample A, A. halotolerans was also reported as ARG host in sample B.",
    "Point mutations were not investigated using the read-based resistome analysis workflow described here.",
    "To investigate the broader genetic context of the FQ ARGs, we performed an assembly-based analysis, and binned the resulting contigs (Figure 1B)."
  ]
}